('dic-j', 'J', 'j-stroke', 'Voiced palato-alveolar affricate. Heavy downward stroke.', 'heavy-down-straight', 'Thick line. As in "jeep" or "gin". Heavy version of CH.', 'PITMAN', 'J'),
