('dic-l', 'L', 'l-stroke', 'Voiced alveolar lateral approximant. Light clockwise curve downward.', 'light-down-curve', 'Light clockwise curve. Written from top to bottom. As in "lie" or "low".', 'PITMAN', 'L'),
