('dic-m', 'M', 'm-stroke', 'Voiced bilabial nasal. Heavy downward curve.', 'heavy-down-curve', 'Heavy clockwise curve. As in "me" or "may". Nasal sound through the nose.', 'PITMAN', 'M'),
