('dic-diph-ow', 'OW (diphthong ow)', 'diphthong-ow', 'Diphthong as in "cow", "how", "now". Upward hook at second place.', 'up-hook', 'Upward hook written at second-place position. A small hook pointing upward.', 'PITMAN', 'ow'),
